{"tid":1648343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界入嚟，急緊法之後我哋係唔係差緊個集體共識","createTime":"2019-10-12T07:11:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:33:33.000Z","uid":57911,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"dd8f04a38281d45bbd116ee281a3df26306de12c","tid":1648343,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:11:55.000Z","msg":"先唔論係唔係有人分化<br />\n好明顯見到和勇兩邊喺緊急法之後係同時剎咗掣<br />\n有人覺得前線有鬼玩到過晒火位<br />\n有人覺得要道歉<br />\n有人覺得咪鬼認頭<br />\n有人覺得唔好理對錯總之要繼續做<br />\n有人覺得成本太高<br />\n各種各樣睇法走晒出嚟<br />\n依幾日完完全全剎晒掣又得唔到一個明確嘅共識<br />\n之前我哋好多嘢都好快有共識<br />\n例如神獸、火法、火牆等等<br />\n唯獨今次裝修俾鬼搞到亂晒<br />\n甚至有文宣想將全部責任推卸俾啲popo<br />\n想講如果推俾popo係唔係即係叫前線唔好再做<br />\n我哋急須一個共識<br />\n一個大家都容許嘅集體意志<br />\n有咗依個集體意志我哋可以走得更遠<br />\n唔洗再爭論咩應該做咩唔應該做<br />\n咁嘅話就唔洗再屌咩分化撚<br />\n軍規算係一種前線共識<br />\n如果有一種論述講到出嚟大家都會明<br />\n就唔需要咁辛苦慢慢磨合<br />\n<br />\n例如之前見到嘅依段<br />\n<br />\n「不分化不割席不篤灰<br />\n罵不還手 只還口<br />\n打不還口 要還手<br />\n<br />\n良心黃店要懲罰<br />\n中資藍店要罷買<br />\n仆街黑店要裝修」"},{"pid":"a74bffe10d97cf8e4dff17ec449c95164f49a709","tid":1648343,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:23:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606b40d6156b62e9736ac8e1cea6016bbcca281c","tid":1648343,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T09:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67c315274901ef796667e291961d15b7b084c947","tid":1648343,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"764ffa5876087d78029b360a51fb4471699633e7","tid":1648343,"uid":287594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"[行動POST] 想要靚畫面？銀髮族48小時靜坐咪就係機會囉<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648992\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648992</a><br />\n<br />\n警總靜坐現場，有老人有中年人有外國人有後生仔。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多中年帶哂席同櫈黎，準備過夜。<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">想有新行動？想要靚畫面？咁你就快啲過黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n今日攰唔出都唔緊要，準備聽日接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同我煲大佢，唔好當銀髮手足係condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zAwXWg8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzAwXWg8.jpg&h=aab0f8a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a22c7fc0543c0cbae85e9a22a196162178071b38","tid":1648343,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T13:03:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0d38bf4c2e3209c6b96c2d3cca33c4df48fa7e4","tid":1648343,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:34:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>｛香港有救｝我有辦法解決連登有鬼亂推活動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648944\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648944</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n啲公眾人物揀晒和理選項都係fail"},{"pid":"34069903ec399530a7524f022e21f66934fc39ca","tid":1648343,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}